{
  "stem": "9102.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because really I couldn't do much at that time yet, because it was still out-- you know, it's just the part where we lived was liberated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as it turned out, her brother who was in-- in the military at the beginning of the war was also hidden.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had two daughters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came to live also with my aunt-- with that aunt I lived with.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was really crowded all around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, fun.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess if you want to call it, basically, probably-- normal, tried to be a normal life, if you want to call it that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I got some friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and all this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, but kind of not in church all the time too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, again, in  '44, I was, you know, 9, 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, you know, you still missed your parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then of course, as you probably know, the-- the rest of Holland still had to [? bet ?] 1945 winter coming.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had no food, nothing, and all this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, finally in 1945, in May, the Germans surrendered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it wasn't long after that that my aunt, not the one I lived with, but the sister of my mother, who had moved up to the northern part of the country in Friesland, in the hiding place, that she managed to get a list of surviving Jews.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why we had to register with the police after we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the lists were all there, what stayed the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she got hold of a list in her part of the country and found that I-- we survived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So didn't take her long to come down-- whatever ways.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no transportation, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
